      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 4,

      "duration_seconds": 1.5,

      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",

      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",

      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"

      "offset_seconds": 43,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Good.",
      "speaker_name": "Lester"

      "offset_seconds": 45,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Can you share your screen?",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"

      "offset_seconds": 49,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Can you see?",
      "speaker_name": "Lester"

      "offset_seconds": 51,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1.5,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "I can't see your screen.",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"

      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "No, wait.",
      "speaker_name": "Lester"

      "offset_seconds": 56,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Hang on.",

      "offset_seconds": 58,

      "description": "Lester looks around, trying to figure out how to share screen."

    {
      "offset_seconds": 103,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Now can you?",
      "speaker_name": "Lester"

      "offset_seconds": 105,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "Not yet.",
      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"

      "offset_seconds": 107,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Um...",
      "speaker_name": "Lester"

      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Hang on. When's... always doing this.",

      "offset_seconds": 117,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 4,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",
      "text": "So, um, how do you do it? Do you see the green button at the very bottom?",

    {
      "offset_seconds": 121,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "speaker_name": "Lester"

      "offset_seconds": 123,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1.5,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Yeah, I'm pushing it.",

      "offset_seconds": 125,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 4,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",

      "offset_seconds": 133,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",

      "offset_seconds": 135,
      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",

      "speaker_name": "Varaun Gandhi"

      "duration_seconds": 3,
      "speaker_label": "tutor",

      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 1,
      "speaker_label": "student",
      "text": "Uh, yeah.",

      "duration_seconds": 3,

      "event_type": "spoken_utterance",
      "duration_seconds": 2,
      "speaker_label": "student",

      "speaker_label": "tutor",
